{"about_the_game":"Sophica: Temples Of Mystery, is a First Person, Puzzle Platformer. <br />\r\nYou wake up in your bed, look outside to see that you are among the clouds.<br />\r\n\u300aIs this a dream?\u300b You continue forward to see what this is about, the mystery lies ahead...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEasy to play, but hard to master.<br />\r\nCan you make it trough all the levels?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nImplemented Features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCrouching<br />\r\nSprinting<br />\r\nDouble jump<br />\r\nMenu working with gamepad<br />\r\nGame also playable with gamepad<br />\r\nSave and load game system<br />\r\nCheckpoint system<br />\r\nInteractive level design (pick up boxes, events, etc.)<br />\r\nDiverse and unique levels<br />\r\nBeautiful and relaxing music<br />\r\nRelaxed gameplay, no timing, no score etc.<br />\r\nPlanned Features after release:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore games to come in the future based on the same game, but with unique levels and evolved gameplay:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Level selection<br />\r\n- Procedural levels<br />\r\n- Create your own levels<br />\r\n- Swimming system<br />\r\n- More ways to interract<br />\r\n- Bigger and different puzzles<br />\r\n- Reward systems<br />\r\n- Complex gravity system for different gravity types and rotating gravity","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1549971136","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017600/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1549971136","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1549971136","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017600/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1549971136","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[